---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="The Boss Playbook Newsletter — Compensation Strategy for Executives"
  description="Free weekly compensation breakdown for GMs, VPs, and senior tech executives. Real numbers, negotiation tactics, and career leverage — no fluff."
>
  <div class="container news">
    <p class="kicker">Boss Playbook</p>
    <h1>The Weekly Compensation Breakdown</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      One email a week for GMs and executives: what roles actually pay, what
      moves the number, and the negotiation tactics that hold up in the room.
      Written by operators, backed by data. Free.
    </p>

    <!-- Beehiiv Email Signup Embed -->
    <div id="beehiiv-embed"></div>
    <script src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/attribution.js"></script>
    <iframe
      src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/pub_61abbf38-efab-4318-9706-bbda7ab10dfb"
      data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
      height="320"
      width="100%"
      frameborder="0"
      scrolling="no"
      style="border-radius: 4px; border: 2px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 0; background-color: transparent;"
    ></iframe>

    <p class="note">
      Or follow <strong>@boss.playbook</strong> on Instagram for daily compensation intel.
    </p>

    <div class="proof card">
      <h2>What subscribers get</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The real 2026 bands for exec roles across 50 US metros — anchored to BLS data, not vibes.</li>
        <li>One negotiation tactic per issue, with the exact language that works at the executive level.</li>
        <li>Equity math explained the way an investor would: 409A, preference stacks, refresh cliffs.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="downloads card">
      <h2>Free Executive Resources</h2>
      <p>Download our free lead magnets — packed with frameworks and tactics you can use immediately.</p>
      <ul class="download-list">
        <li>
          <a href="/downloads/salary-negotiation-playbook.pdf" download class="download-link">
            📄 The Salary Negotiation Playbook for Executives
            <span class="dl-badge">Free PDF</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/downloads/gm-90-day-ramp.docx" download class="download-link">
            📄 The GM 90-Day Ramp Playbook
            <span class="dl-badge">Free Download</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/downloads/exec-comp-truths.docx" download class="download-link">
            📄 Executive Comp Truths They Don't Tell You
            <span class="dl-badge">Free Download</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .news { max-width: 640px; text-align: center; padding-top: 3rem; }
  .kicker {
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lede { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .note { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .proof { margin-top: 2.5rem; text-align: left; }
  .proof h2 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .proof ul { margin-left: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem; }
  .proof li { line-height: 1.65; font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  .downloads { margin-top: 2rem; text-align: left; }
  .downloads h2 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .downloads p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .download-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .download-link {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
    border-radius: var(--radius); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .download-link:hover { background: #e0f2fe; text-decoration: none; }
  .dl-badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
